g 'Umrah will expiate whatever sins were committed between them, and the blessed Hajj pilgrimage has no reward other than Paradise.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1773, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1349 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15618,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/08\/07\/reward-children-hajj-umrah\/","url_meta":{"origin":9969,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Hajj: Taking children to the pilgrimage","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 7, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: A woman lifted up her child and said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, is the Hajj pilgrimage for this child?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cYes, you will have a reward.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1336 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0633\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40536,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/07\/03\/women-hajj-menstruation\/","url_meta":{"origin":9969,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Menses: Women performing Hajj will menstruating","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 3, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, enter my dwelling at Sarif while I was crying. The Prophet said, \u201cWhat is the matter? Are you menstruating?\u201d I said yes. The Prophet said, \u201cThis is a matter that Allah has decreed for the daughters of Adam,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20884,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/09\/09\/kind-words-peace-feed\/","url_meta":{"origin":9969,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Charity: Speak kind words, offer peace, feed poor","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 9, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Shurayh reported: He said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, tell me something that will guarantee Paradise for me.\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSpeak kind words, offer peace, and feed the hungry.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 509 Grade: Jayyid (very good) according to Al-Albani\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15610,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/08\/07\/ramadan-umrah-hajj\/","url_meta":{"origin":9969,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Pilgrimage: &#8216;Umrah in Ramadan equal to Hajj","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 7, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Verily, the 'Umrah pilgrimage during Ramadan is equal to Hajj.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1782, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1